00:16:42,169 --> 00:16:44,438
详细解释了为何
which explains exactly why

335
00:16:44,505 --> 00:16:46,974
有关资料库的任何新举措必须暂缓
any newmoves on the Data Base

336
00:16:46,974 --> 00:16:48,275
如果你没能发现
must be delayed. If you don't find it,

337
00:16:48,442 --> 00:16:51,645
