00:24:28,669 --> 00:24:32,105
它汇集了许多有才干的无私奉献的人们
It's staffed by a lot of talented, dedicated people

481
00:24:32,406 --> 00:24:35,676
正尽其所能帮助政府
who do everything in theirpower to help the Government

482
00:24:35,843 --> 00:24:37,511
将政策转化为法律
make it's policies into law.

483
00:24:38,612 --> 00:24:41,348
感谢您所做的广告 大臣
Well, thank you forthe commercial, Minister.

484
00:24:42,015 --> 00:24:44,318
我们现在可以开始节目了吗?
Perhaps we can start the programme now?

485
00:24:44,685 --> 00:24:46,386
