00:25:10,277 --> 00:25:11,645
其次
Secondly,

494
00:25:12,646 --> 00:25:16,150
没有大臣的许可 任何公务员将无权
no civil servant will be allowed to examine personal files

495
00:25:16,150 --> 00:25:18,952
查阅其他部门的私人档案
from anotherdepartment, without written authorityfrom a Minister.

496
00:25:19,119 --> 00:25:22,756
我在此宣布 下周将通过一项法案
And I shall be announcing in the House next week legislation

497
00:25:22,923 --> 00:25:26,360
授权公民能向任何未经许可
